jcr:root.jcr:description: This is the Globally Reusable version of the External Use Files Component. It is just a stub as we don't expect that we will need to make any changes, but in the event that we do we want to make sure that we have insulated ourselves from other streams making changes that could negatively affect the brands individually.
jcr:root.jcr:title: Mattel Global External Use Files Component
